<h4 id="graph-1">Graph #1</h4>

<p>Create a bar chart depicting the number of smokers in Canada. Your chart must be a sliding bar chart. It can be horizontal or vertical.</p>

<h4 id="graph-2">Graph #2</h4>

<p>Create a pie chart with the provided data.</p>

